<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img alt="" class="wp-image-147969" height="403" src="https://i0.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2025/08/MPC-HackathonNYC-20250816_884-1024x683.jpg?resize=604%2C403&#038;quality=89&#038;ssl=1" width="604" /></figure>



